{"tid":2029214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［524］香港人做一次和理勇好嗎？","createTime":"2020-05-22T06:40:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T10:23:20.000Z","uid":311486,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b7a29ddd1635dcad669fb154665a13761a5cc6f9","tid":2029214,"uid":311486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:40:36.000Z","msg":"大家仲記唔記個日7月1日我地係死守條龍和道等立會手足出番黎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6F2xfnmQBjA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6F2xfnmQBjA&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=12b33666\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6F2xfnmQBjA</a><br />\n大家仲記唔記機場個陣我地係點樣走？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CtLYKUs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCtLYKUs.jpg&h=58f1072d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家仲記唔記得727光復元朗個陣係幾多手足入黎報仇？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dFoO68q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdFoO68q.jpg&h=522fe577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5月24日將會係人民歸來嘅日子<br />\n我地將會比2014 2016 2019更強大<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">面對極權 我地唔會有任何一絲畏懼</span><br />\n今仗 我地不分勇武 不分和理非<br />\n每一個人都係為香港而戰 我地係香港人 我地係和理勇<br />\n如果要殺死我地香港人 麻煩殺死我地200萬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b8c30e08b10935a2b171095f15454ee32a23bf","tid":2029214,"uid":311486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:41:43.000Z","msg":"見到呢個po嘅人 拿拿聲同我airdrop文宣 share文宣 再叫埋老豆老母 小學同學星期日出黎！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de92517a927baf6edfa1f0e898ef60690a2ec87","tid":2029214,"uid":32836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:53:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"890ea457ab4b0ec877f03dd1ca4e490b1230a23f","tid"